<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">إِذَا قَالَ:</span> إِنْ كَلَّمْتُكِ فَأَنْتِ طَالِقٌ فَتَحَقَّقِي،<span class="c5"> أَوْ قَالَ:</span> تَنَحَّيْ،<span class="c5"> أَوِ اسْكُتِي:</span> طَلَقَتْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِنْ بَدَأْتُكِ بِالكَلَامِ فَأَنْتِ طَالِقٌ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَتْ:</span> إِنْ بَدَأْتُكَ بِهِ فَعَبْدِي حُرٌّ: انْحَلَّتْ يَمِينُهُ، مَا لَمْ يَنْوِ عَدَمَ البَدَاءَةِ فِي مَجْلِسٍ آخَرَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>